  <summary date="2005-03-10T19:49:23Z" status="Introduced in House">More Money for College Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) eliminate the dollar limitation applicable to the tax deduction for qualified tuition and related expenses; (2) deny such deduction for taxpayers with adjusted gross incomes exceeding $80,000 ($160,000 for joint returns), adjusted for inflation; and (3) make such deduction permanent.</summary>
